result.name: Pak Don

reviews.text: The boneless chicken taste good. However, the waitress was rude and unhelpful when I made my order. Won't be there next time

I love this chicken rice restaurant so much! The chicken is nice every single time I go for a meal! It's a small place and sometimes there will be full of people. So I'll only recommend when you're alone or with only 1-2 people. I love the combination of chicken and port patty! All sauces for the chicken are super nice! The sweet soy sauce is really something! It tastes like plums or some fruity stuff, but in a good way. You can't miss it if you like chicken rice! You can choose a canton soup for drink or I'll always do the lemon tea. The soup is so good too.
Not real Singaporean style, probably Hong Kong Siu Mei style but the texture of chicken still great
Their boneless chicken is sooo good. Especially with the green sauce.
Touch Chicken with Dry Chicken Oil Rice. Black Soy Sauce is Thin

result.name: 栢檔極品海南雞飯

reviews.text: 午餐豬頸肉，豬腳肉，海南雞，肉餅，肉骨茶，肉骨茶唔淡好甜，湯色中等濃，不過藥味少，甜係加左好多紅棗甜，沒有自己煮的好味

好一般！ 油飯望落幾靚，但食落亳無油飯香，食左半碗就無食，雞無雞味，肉質尚算正常唔算特別鞋， 環境坐得唔舒服，吧台坐係咁俾人撞，一個年記最大既大陸口音女人態度冷淡，講野無尾音，面無笑容好似差左佢錢咁。
三色海南雞醬幾香，但係個海南雞黑醬油食落有陣京都念慈奄既味，不如用返出面現成果d 啦，無下次

值得讚既就係佢坐埋位後佢會拎杯熱水俾你。
一間比得上曼谷的風味餐廳，價錢又不貴，地點方便，正！
好耐冇食，出奇地少人，加左3蚊價，味道保持水準
佐敦依間海南鷄飯做招牌口感味道唔错，尤以酱料味道喺近期佳作！不過其他菜兴趣不大，今日餐湯好难饮，猪臊味太重喇。
